<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>2502</hymn_number>
<author>Gaetano Caruso</author>
<title>You gotta know</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 You gotta know Jesus
 Before you go
 You gonna find Jesus
 And give your life
 To Jesus

[V2]
 You gotta call Jesus
 You gonna say Jesus
 You gotta pray Jesus
 Please come and stay

[V3]
 He came for you and for me
 To make the blind see
 To make the dead arise
 And all the lost to find
 To change your sadness to joy
 And leave your past behind
 To start a brand new day
 And live with no compromise

[V4]
 Heaven and earth
 Under control
 No fear to hide
 He will provide</lyrics>
</song>